title: Allocate 15% Of Treasury for Hyper-Growth and Funding a Bigger Team
body:
You, the JADE community, will vote on whether or not 15% of our treasury will be used for these benefits: 

1. Aggressively growing our team — we want to continue bringing in geniuses from all around the world. Priority #1 is expanding our dev team.

2. Allowing our team to quit their day jobs — several devs still have a day job, and some are even running entire businesses. Incentivizing them to go “all in” with us will require capital. 

All uses of the Growth Fund will be on a public ledger. A link will be posted on our Gitbook.

If this vote passes, we believe it will have a significantly positive impact on the JADE ecosystem. More industry-leading devs we can hire. A full-time, round-the-clock committed team.

We believe the price impact of this decision is incredibly bullish. We’re thinking about the 10+ year future of our ecosystem. Having a reliable way to attract the smartest people to fully commit is critical. 

Dedicating 15% of our treasury is our solution.

For full details, see our forthcoming Medium post here: https://medium.com/@SmartCoin
